WASHINGTON (WUSA9) -- NFL football on WUSA9! 
Week six of the season and a CBS NFL doubleheader Sunday. 
Cincinnati @ Buffalo at 1 p.m. and Ravens @ 49ers at 4:25 p.m. 
Will The Bengals remain undefeated? 
Ravens and 49ers both need a win. What team will improve to 2-4? 
Tune in Sunday to find out!
